      <title>参议员对派遣国民警卫队平息校园抗议持谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/senators-wary-of-sending-national-guard-to-quell-campus-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国参议员驳回了众议院议长迈克·约翰逊的建议，即向大学校园派遣国民警卫队，以平息日益增长的反对加沙战争和美国支持以色列的抗议活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/senators-wary-of-sending-national-guard-to-quell-campus-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 17:59:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
